INSERT INTO public.tojung (id,num,total,jan,feb,mar,apr,may,jun,jul,aug,sep,oct,nov,"dec",created_at,nation) VALUES (434,'065','âœ¨ 1. 2026 Overall Fortune
The year 2026 will be one of change and patience. Like a great hawk spreading its wings to fly, if you miss the right timing, difficulties may follow. In the beginning, you must abandon impatience and act prudently, as hasty decisions can be harmful. Worries may arise and joy may fade, but if you endure and persevere, you will overcome early difficulties and good fortune will come in the latter half. Thanks to ancestral blessings, worries will turn to joy in the second half, wealth fortune will flourish, and positive energy will return.

âœ¨ 2. ğŸ’° Wealth and Financial Fortune
Financial fortune in 2026 is somewhat unstable in the beginning but improves toward the latter half. Wealth may come from ventures started by chance, but avoid risky investments or irregular methods. Particularly, stable profits can be expected from land or real estate rather than water-related businesses. Small gains may occur in April and September, but they may fall short of expectations, so avoid greed. Unexpected expenses may arise in May and June, so pay attention to financial management. From November onward, financial fortune recovers, allowing you to end the year stably.

âœ¨ 3. ğŸ† Career and Promotion Fortune
In the professional field, this is a year requiring patience and perseverance. Early on, there may be lack of cooperation and things may not go as planned, but if you don''t give up and work steadily, you can see results in the second half. Starting new businesses or projects requires caution, and it''s better to approach them with the mindset of gaining experience rather than success. Don''t trust others carelessly and proceed by verifying yourself. What appears kind on the surface may have different intentions inside, so important work decisions must be made carefully. Opportunities to reap the fruits of your efforts will come in October and November.

âœ¨ 4. â¤ï¸ Love and Marriage Fortune
Romance fortune is generally modest. Singles should get to know their partners slowly rather than rushing to advance relationships. Misunderstandings or conflicts may arise in March and April, so pay attention to communication and listen to your partner. Married couples need patience and effort to understand each other in their relationship. Focusing on family harmony in June and July can improve relationships. After September, stability will be found and trust in each other will deepen.

âœ¨ 5. ğŸ¥ Health Fortune
This is a year requiring special attention to health management. In February and March, weakened immunity due to overwork or stress is a concern, so get sufficient rest. Particular attention is needed for digestive and respiratory illnesses, and maintaining health through regular meals and exercise is important. In June, worries may arise from health problems of family members, so regular checkups are recommended. If you pray sincerely and maintain peace of mind, you can overcome difficulties. In the second half, health conditions will gradually recover and find stability.

âœ¨ 6. ğŸ‘¥ Relationship Fortune
In relationships, this is a time requiring prudence. Even people who appear kind on the surface may have different intentions, so don''t trust easily. Especially regarding wealth or important matters, it''s wise to judge for yourself rather than blindly believing others'' words. In March and August, you may get caught up in misunderstandings or gossip, so be careful with words. However, after September, relationships with genuine people will deepen and mutually helpful relationships will form. It''s good to maintain appropriate distance even with close people and observe courtesy.

âœ¨ 7. ğŸ“š Academic and Self-Development Fortune
In academics and self-development, consistency is key. Initially, you may feel frustrated as results are not visible, but if you don''t give up and continue working, you can achieve good results in the latter half. Rather than challenging new fields, it''s advantageous to deepen existing studies. In May and October, concentration increases and learning efficiency improves, so utilize these periods well. Certification acquisition or exam preparation is more favorable in the second half, and steady effort will bear fruit. It''s important not to be impatient and maintain your own pace.','January is a month requiring prudence. Like trying to catch fish in the mountains, goals and methods don''t match, leading to wasted effort. Without a set direction in mind, you wander here and there, so it''s important to clarify goals and make plans first.

Even trying to start new businesses or projects for the new year may not go well, so don''t push hastily. This is a period difficult to complete tasks or achieve results. At work, you may feel frustrated as tasks don''t proceed smoothly, but if you endure and stay faithful to basics, gradual improvement will come from next month.

Wealth fortune is unstable. Avoiding large expenses and focusing on savings is wise. Health-wise, beware of winter colds and indigestion, and manage your body warmly. In relationships, be careful with words and avoid unnecessary promises. Approach with a calm attitude of planning and preparing for the year.','February is a month showing signs of change but still accompanied by difficulties. Like a maple tree meeting autumn, it appears splendid but lacks substance. In unfavorable fortune, the family becomes unstable and unexpected illness or health problems may occur.

Continuing discomfort in both body and mind may lead to feelings of emptiness and depression. In such times, praying sincerely and controlling your mind is important. Visiting famous mountains or temples to seek peace of mind can help escape difficulties.

Wealth fortune is also poor, so avoid risky investments or business expansion. At work, misunderstandings may arise in relationships with superiors or colleagues, so act prudently. Pay special attention to health management, especially carefully observe the condition of elderly or health-weak family members. If you endure and wait for the right time, gradual improvement will come from next month.','March is a month of endless worries. Unable to achieve aspirations, with household troubles, the mind cannot find peace. Even trying to leave home to soothe your mind, other difficulties await, so be cautious.

There is no benefit outside, so staying home and enduring is wise. Rather than new attempts, focus on current work and strengthen fundamentals. Excessive external activities may actually cause losses.

Wealth fortune remains unstable, and unexpected expenses may occur, so pay attention to financial management. At work, postpone major changes or new project launches, and focus on stably performing existing duties. Health-wise, beware of spring seasonal colds and allergies, and get sufficient rest.

In relationships, avoiding conflict and staying quiet is advantageous. Cherish time with family and strive to maintain harmony. Though difficult times, if you endure and wait, situations will gradually improve from next month.','April is a month when unexpected opportunities arrive. Wealth may come from ventures started by chance, but won''t be as large as expected. Avoid water-related work as it''s unfavorable, and seek stable profits in land or real estate-related matters.

Signs of gradually recovering wealth fortune appear, but even trying to achieve desired goals, incoming profits may fall short of expectations. Avoid greed, be satisfied with small gains, and maintain a steady working attitude.

At work, tasks gradually find stability, and working sincerely can earn recognition from superiors. Rather than new projects, focus on completing existing work with quality. Health-wise, spring fatigue may accumulate, so pay attention to sufficient sleep and nutrition intake.

Relationships are smooth, but wisdom is needed to judge for yourself rather than easily believing others'' words. Increasing conversation time with family and broadening understanding will improve relationships. Don''t be impatient and proceed step by step.','May is a month when setbacks occur in nearly completed tasks, like a bright moon unexpectedly covered by clouds. Coveting wealth through irregular methods can actually bring harm, so be careful. Unexpected difficulties may strike ongoing ventures.

Slight failures or setbacks may occur in well-progressing work, and small losses may be experienced along the way. However, if you stick to honest and legitimate methods, major damage can be avoided. It''s important to abandon greed and maintain principles.

At work, plans may go awry due to unexpected variables, so respond flexibly. Strengthen communication with superiors and colleagues, and if problems arise, report immediately to find solutions together. Health-wise, pay attention to stress management and maintain fitness through regular exercise.

Wealth fortune is unstable, so refrain from investments or large expenses, and focus wisely on savings and financial organization. In relationships, misunderstandings or conflicts may arise, so be careful with words and avoid unnecessary promises.','June is a month requiring sincere prayer. Without visiting temples or famous mountains to pray, suffering from illness may visit the household. Being close to people with surnames Lee or Park may help in gaining wealth.

There is risk of legal troubles, so it''s better not to leave for distant places, and if travel or business trips were planned, reconsidering is wise. You may lose wealth on the way or encounter unexpected accidents, so be careful.

At work, beware of legal problems or regulation violations, and handle everything according to principles and regulations. Even small mistakes can escalate into major problems, so act carefully. Pay special attention to health management and carefully observe health conditions of family members.

Wealth fortune is still poor, so economize and reduce unnecessary expenses. In relationships, avoid conflict and stay quiet, and have time for meditation or prayer for peace of mind. If you devote sincerity, you can overcome difficulties.','July is a month when body and mind are uncomfortable, like a chicken bird meeting frost on a cold day. Ongoing work is like flowers without roots, bringing no joy despite effort. Going to distant places is unfavorable, so keep your place and organize body and mind.

Realize that everything depends on the mind, and focus on finding inner peace rather than external environment. Rather than excessive activities or new attempts, maintaining the current situation and finding stability is wise.

At work, don''t have high expectations and focus on faithfully performing assigned duties. Rather than pursuing change, focusing on maintaining status quo is advantageous. Wealth fortune is poor, so economize and spend according to plan.

Health-wise, beware of fatigue from summer heat and humidity, and protect health with sufficient rest and water intake. In relationships, avoid conflict and have time alone to control your mind. Build inner strength through meditation or reading.','August is a month of seeking results without haste in work but failing to achieve them. Even trying to undertake new work won''t match ongoing work, so it''s wise to consistently focus on one thing and expect good results.

However, results obtained compared to the start may be less than expected, so don''t have too high expectations. An attitude of being grateful even for small achievements and working steadily is needed. Abandon impatience and approach with patience.

At work, perform duties stably, but avoid new projects or changes. Building trust through sincerity and responsibility will bring good opportunities later. Wealth fortune is ordinary, so don''t be greedy and live within current income.

Health is smooth but avoiding overwork and maintaining regular life is important. In relationships, spend naturally without high expectations and find small pleasures with close people. Slow but steady steps will eventually reach the goal.','September is a month with great ambitions but insignificant results. Like trying to draw a tiger but ending up with a dog, you may be disappointed by the difference between expectations and reality. However, news from the north may accidentally bring harm, so be careful.

Starting new business may bring in wealth, so carefully reviewing and starting on a small scale is also good. It''s worth spreading your wings once, but greed is forbidden.

At work, rather than ambitious plans, set realistic goals and execute step by step. Even small achievements, when accumulated, can lead to major results later. Signs of gradually recovering wealth fortune appear, but caution is still needed.

Health-wise, beware of seasonal colds and weakened immunity, and protect health through regular exercise and sufficient nutrition intake. In relationships, listen to others'' advice with a humble attitude, and approaching with a learning mindset will help. Don''t be disappointed and move forward with a positive mind.','October is a month without strength to gauge body and mind, like the sun setting over western mountains and losing the way back. Nothing attempted works out, and unexpected difficulties may strike, causing losses or harm.

During this period, rather than new attempts, focus on maintaining status quo and refrain from excessive activities is wise. Both physical and mental strength may weaken, so get sufficient rest and pay special attention to health management.

At work, mistakes or failures may be experienced, but don''t blame yourself too much and take them as learning opportunities. Asking for help from superiors or colleagues is also a good method. Wealth fortune is very unfavorable, so absolutely avoid investments or large expenses.

Health-wise, beware of illnesses from overwork and stress, and if necessary, taking vacation to rest sufficiently is good. In relationships, avoid conflict and stay quiet, focusing on finding mental stability. Though difficult times, they will soon pass, so endure.','November is a month when difficult times pass and good fortune returns. Good things will surely come, and yin and yang harmonize, allowing you to safely overcome difficult matters. Wealth flourishes and worries disappear, with good fortune bringing fullness of joy.

Efforts so far begin to bear fruit, so move forward toward your goals with full strength. Acting actively with confidence can bring good results. Wealth fortune rises greatly, income increases, and financial status will stabilize.

At work, work performance is recognized and opportunities for promotion or awards may come. Challenging new projects is good, and creative ideas can earn good evaluations. Health also recovers, overflowing with vitality and positive energy.

Relationships also become harmonious, and you can reconcile with long-estranged people or meet new connections. Giving to those around you with a grateful heart will bring more blessings. Actively seize opportunities.','December is a month when you shouldn''t trust others. Trusting and associating with others can actually cause great harm, so be cautious. With obstacles in a hundred matters, though you have the heart to work and achieve, it''s difficult to gain results proportional to effort.

Staying home is auspicious and going far brings harm, so refrain from unnecessary outings or travel and find stability at home is wise. Though the year-end will be busy, don''t overdo it and pay attention to health management.

At work, rather than major changes or new attempts, focus on wrapping up existing work and gradually prepare for next year. Wealth fortune weakens somewhat compared to November, so avoid overspending and economize.

Health-wise, beware of accumulated fatigue from year-end gatherings and overwork, and get sufficient rest. In relationships, rather than excessive trust, maintain appropriate distance and focus on your own matters is advantageous. Approach with an attitude of organizing the year and preparing for next year.','2025-03-02 12:02:33.536145+00','e');
